pageProduct.name: Swisse Propolis 2000mg 210 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Propolis is a premium quality formula to support general health and wellbeing in a convenient, one-a-day dose.

General Health: Propolis maintains general health and wellbeing. It has been used for centuries in Western and Eastern medicine.

Antioxidant Support: Propolis is a source of antioxidants to help reduce free radical damage to body cells.

Size: 210 capsules

Warnings

Propolis may cause allergic reactions. If irritation or swelling of the mouth or throat occurs - discontinue use.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:PROPOLIS dry extract 400 mg equiv. propolis 2g.

PROPOLIS dry extract equiv. to fresh 2 g

Allergen Contains: Phenylalanine| Propolis| Soybean| Sulphites

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE: One capsule daily or as directed by your healthcare professional.

One capsule daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.
